title: Staffer in Washington, D.C., mayor's office charge for puported cocaine distribution
text: A staffer in the Washington, D.C., mayoral office has been arrested for cocaine distribution after police purportedly found more than 120 grams of cocaine, suspected heroin and drug-related paraphernalia, according to news reports. ...
